OL,3,CFirst 'bionic peer' enters House of
OL,4,CLords, vowing to fight for sepsis
OL,5,Csurvivors
OL,7,FITV News Politics Reporter Jasmine
OL,8,FCameron-Chileshe reports that Craig
OL,9,FMackinlay takes up his peerage in the
OL,10,FLords, he will now campaign to raise
OL,11,Fawareness about the disease so it can
OL,12,Fbe spotted earlier and treated better
OL,14,FThe House of Lords' first ever
OL,15,F"bionic" peer has said he is
OL,16,Fdetermined to raise awareness of
OL,17,Fsepsis and has vowed to improve the
OL,18,Fquality of prosthetics offered to
OL,19,Ffellow amputees.
