OL,5,Csurvivors
OL,7,FSpeaking on life after sepsis, he
OL,8,Fsaid: "You're reliant on other people,
OL,9,Fand you do get frustrated, and I've
OL,10,Fnever been the most patient of
OL,11,Fcharacters even before this. So yes,
OL,12,Fit's difficult.
OL,14,F"But there's two things that keep me
OL,15,Fgoing really, I can do more things
OL,16,Ftoday than I could do yesterday, so
OL,17,FI'll be able to do more tomorrow. And,
OL,18,Fyou've got to say well it's better
OL,19,Fthan the alternative, and I was very
OL,20,Fclose to the alternative, which was
OL,21,Fdeath."
