OL,7,FOn an episode of a podcast called The
OL,8,FSepsis Voices with Dr Ron, Lord
OL,9,FMackinlay described himself as a
OL,10,F"bionic Lord" due to his prosthetics.
OL,12,FHe has pledged to "battle" with the
OL,13,FHealth Secretary on working to ensure
OL,14,Famputees receive adequate prosthetic
OL,15,Flimbs, condemning a "postcode lottery"
OL,16,Fsystem currently faced by those
OL,17,Frelying on the NHS.
