OL,7,FHe said: "The NHS work off a list:
OL,8,Fyear one you'll have these rubber,
OL,9,Fblunt instruments. Year two, they
OL,10,Fmight give you a body-powered thing
OL,11,Fthat looks like something out of
OL,12,FVictorian times.
OL,14,F"And year three they might start
OL,15,Ftalking about electric ones that you
OL,16,Freally wanted in the first place. So
OL,17,Fwhat are you meant to do for those
OL,18,Fthree years? Go into a total mental
OL,19,Fhealth hole?"
