OL,7,FHe said: He added: "The trouble is
OL,8,Fthere's not really a one size fits all
OL,9,Fmenu, not really, but to try and get
OL,10,Fan awareness early, because sepsis
OL,11,Fkills 48,000 people a year, it's a
OL,12,Fhuge killer in the UK.
OL,14,F"We devote a lot of time to looking at
OL,15,Fother diseases, but not quite the same
OL,16,Fto this mass killer."
OL,18,FHe said he was grateful for the
OL,19,Fsupport of his family, particularly
OL,20,Fhis five-year-old daughter.
